{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"7e374689e8","title":"对《中国人民革命胜利经验的基本总结》一文的批语和修改","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"e647654538","index":1,"year":1960,"month":10,"day":29,"articleId":"7e374689e8"},{"id":"ed914b8d85","index":0,"year":1960,"month":10,"day":28,"articleId":"7e374689e8"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji44","name":"毛泽东全集第44卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/44-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji44":{"comments":[{"id":"f4bfd9ac8a","publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"7e374689e8","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这篇文章是《红旗》杂志编辑部为《毛泽东选集》第四卷出版而作的，发表在1960年11月1日出版的《红旗》杂志第二十、二十一期合刊上。"},{"id":"ce411eb286","publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"7e374689e8","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"田家英，当时任中共中央政治研究室副主任、《红旗》杂志常务编辑、毛泽东的秘书。"},{"id":"81f49c1de6","publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"7e374689e8","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"本篇三、四、五中用宋体字排印的是毛泽东加写和改写的文字。"},{"id":"81499939e4","publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"7e374689e8","index":4,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"伯达，即陈伯达，当时任中共中央政治研究室主任、《红旗》杂志总编辑、毛泽东的秘书。"}],"contents":[{"id":"89824b35db","type":"title","text":"对《中国人民革命胜利经验的基本总结》“一文的批语和修改","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"7e374689e8"},{"id":"f4bfd9ac8a","type":"paragraph","text":"田家英同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"7e374689e8"},{"id":"ce411eb286","type":"paragraph","text":"写得很好，略有修改问，请你及伯达同志加以翻的。如认为可以，即可付印。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"7e374689e8"},{"id":"81f49c1de6","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"7e374689e8"},{"id":"81499939e4","type":"paragraph","text":"十月廿八日上午","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"7e374689e8"},{"id":"d3fbaa7ed9","type":"paragraph","text":"退田家英同志照办","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"7e374689e8"},{"id":"cdeef07ec1","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"7e374689e8"},{"id":"050e822388","type":"paragraph","text":"十月廿九日上午","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"7e374689e8"},{"id":"125b513244","type":"subtitle","text":"三","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"7e374689e8"},{"id":"2ff1468776","type":"paragraph","text":"另一方面，在我们的革命队伍中，当时有一批小资产阶级的“左”倾冒险主义者，他们在好几年内占领了党的领导机关，把以毛泽东同志为首的大批正确领导同志打下去，使这些同志抬不起头来。“左”倾冒险主义者否认中国革命斗争的长期性和曲折性，看不到中国革命必须经过的由小到大、由农村到城市的发展过程，急于夺取大城市。","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"7e374689e8"},{"id":"81b3faa398","type":"subtitle","text":"四","index":10,"publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"7e374689e8"},{"id":"ac7485c727","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东同志在一九三五年反对“左”倾冒险主义的胜利，在当时革命力量削弱到只剩下十分之一的情况下，迅速地重振起来，保证中国革命走上了健全发展的道路。","index":11,"publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"7e374689e8"},{"id":"ed1c9a77cd","type":"subtitle","text":"五","index":12,"publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"7e374689e8"},{"id":"3dc62a078a","type":"paragraph","text":"国民党反动派千方百计地企图破坏和摧毁革命人民的国家机器，而革命人民的神圣任务，就是保卫、发展和强化这个革命的国家机器，以达到打倒日本帝国主义，并在随后打倒那敢于向革命力量进攻的国民党反动派的革命目的。","index":13,"publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"7e374689e8"}],"page":{"id":"31f2a6604a","publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"7e374689e8","start":49,"end":51}}}},"__N_SSG":true}